item.title: CVE-2023-30521|2024-08-02T14:28:51.621Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20assembla%20merge%20request%20builder%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Assembla merge request builder Plugin 1.1.13 and earlier allows unauthenticated attackers to trigger builds of jobs corresponding to the attacker-specified repository.
